WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.099 --> 00:00:02.264
[ Laughter ] -Yeah.

00:00:02.264 --> 00:00:04.000
-Oh, this was so fun. Let's do it again.

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:05.330
-E-mail me that thing. It sounds really interesting.

00:00:05.330 --> 00:00:07.000
-Absolutely. You're gonna love it, John.

00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:08.627
[ Laughter ] -Exciting.

00:00:08.627 --> 00:00:10.396
-Oh, I don't want to go, but I guess we should.

00:00:10.396 --> 00:00:12.099
-Yeah. -Beggaty-boom-boom!

00:00:12.099 --> 00:00:15.363
[ Laughter ]

00:00:15.363 --> 00:00:18.099
-[ Sighs ] -I can't stand them.

00:00:18.099 --> 00:00:19.759
-No, I don't. I don't know. -I can't stand --

00:00:19.759 --> 00:00:21.429
Why do we even invite them?!

00:00:21.429 --> 00:00:23.330
-Don't look at me, okay? 'Cause I didn't invite them.

00:00:23.330 --> 00:00:25.396
-You didn't exactly play defense, either, did you?

00:00:25.396 --> 00:00:27.132
-Really? It was either them come here,

00:00:27.132 --> 00:00:29.297
or us drive all the way across town to their house.

00:00:29.297 --> 00:00:30.528
-Because those are the only two options we have.

00:00:30.528 --> 00:00:31.726
Good job. -Really?

00:00:31.726 --> 00:00:34.099
-Yeah. -Oh, okay. Look,

00:00:34.099 --> 00:00:37.099
I know you like flirting with her!

00:00:37.099 --> 00:00:39.495
[ Soft music plays ]

00:01:02.198 --> 00:01:04.165
-Seriously, why don't we hang out with them more often?

00:01:04.165 --> 00:01:05.396
-I don't know. They're fun, right?

00:01:05.396 --> 00:01:07.099
-Yeah, totally!

00:01:07.099 --> 00:01:08.561
Hey, next time, let's have them over to our place.

00:01:08.561 --> 00:01:10.561
-Yes, definitely. The drive's not that bad.

00:01:10.561 --> 00:01:11.759
-It's not. And isn't Joe

00:01:11.759 --> 00:01:13.561
the sweetest guy ever?

00:01:13.561 --> 00:01:15.033
-Don't you just kind of want them to be our best friends?

00:01:15.033 --> 00:01:16.594
-Yes, I do. -Yes, I do.

00:01:16.594 --> 00:01:18.165
You think they're saying the same thing

00:01:18.165 --> 00:01:19.561
about us, like, right now?

00:01:19.561 --> 00:01:21.363
-Um, I bet we're back over here tomorrow night.

00:01:21.363 --> 00:01:23.165
-I agree wholeheartedly. -[ Chuckles ]

00:01:23.165 --> 00:01:27.033
-[ Humming ]

00:01:27.033 --> 00:01:30.330
Let your fingers do the walkin',

00:01:30.330 --> 00:01:33.132
Thinkin' and the talkin'

00:01:33.132 --> 00:01:35.264
[ Mumbling ]

00:01:35.264 --> 00:01:36.726
when you just can't quite decide which way to go.

00:01:36.726 --> 00:01:40.033
Road champ. -Like, the way you spoke to me,

00:01:40.033 --> 00:01:42.297
and it's not -- It's the how.

00:01:42.297 --> 00:01:45.660
It's like just speak to me like I'm your equal

00:01:45.660 --> 00:01:48.693
and... [ Sighs ]

